&lt;li&gt;Own the entire booking pipeline and identify high-value opportunities (e.g. large groups, special requirements, time-sensitive leads) before anyone asks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively listen, diagnose, and advise tenants and landlords to create smart, win-win matches that deliver value for all sides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multitask across multiple leads and landlords at the same time, always prioritizing based on revenue impact and KPIs, not just order of arrival.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the go-to interface between tenants and landlords, handling complex situations with confidence and pushing opportunities forward to close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data and KPIs to steer your daily decisions, track performance, and consistently exceed targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share insights from your conversations to improve our product, processes, and customer strategy—you are the voice of both tenants and landlords inside the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously optimize how you work and contribute directly to the success and growth of Wunderflats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
